{"books":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":[""],"article":{"title":"无题","authors":["吕学正","重庆大学"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":6}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"text":"无题","type":"title"},{"text":"重庆大学吕学正","type":"authors"},{"text":"[编者按：吕学正，重庆大学学生，其家庭犯过五毒。在这首诗里，吕学正打着为祖国、为人民的幌子，反对党、咒诅今天的社会；甚至说：“一定要消灭你们，直到你们最后一个死去”，字里行间，无处不流露出他对新社会的刻骨仇恨。]","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"(一)","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"闭嘴","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"扯荒的人应该消灭","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我们","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"坚强","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"勇敢","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"要把自己的劳动贡献给祖国","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"你的话语","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"任怎样灿烂","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"和飞着彩色的光彩","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"只要是企图给人民的头上","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"套上那沉重的锁炼","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"就滚去","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"不然——","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我们为了人类的尊严","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"为了祖国","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"和","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"全体社会上的人民——","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"幸福的劳动者","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"一定要消灭你们","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"直到你们最后一个死去","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"不然  　就让我们死去","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"(二)","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"积极就是斗争    消极就是建设","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"应该斗争","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"粗暴","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"勇猛","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"残酷","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"不向敌人低头","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"就夺过他的武器","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"就狠狠你的心","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"二十世纪——暴浪的时代","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"1．加强政治学习","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"2．加强锻炼身体","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"3．牢固掌握科学知识","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"看看说明了什么","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"坐下了一个又起来一个","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"敌人窥视着我的眼光","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"狠恶    冷寞","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"他沉默","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"为什么我喧嚣","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"压制住热情","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"正如是四季开花","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"……","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"(三)","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"恶风吹来了乌云","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"落叶暗示了深秋","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"在魅人的广野","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"残零剥夺了伟壮","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"丑恶掩没着美丽的","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"天！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"不再呈现出玉蓝","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"夜","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"不再充溢着清辉","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"海","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"不再闪着蓝光","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"花","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"不再微笑","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"嗨","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"破碎年青的心","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"消灭太阳吧","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"在生命没有告别时","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我们不会碎裂","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"等待她死亡","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"失望吧","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"她会永生","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"年青的心激动呀","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"(四)","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"你失败  它兴奋","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"不让爱你的人们流泪","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"武装起来呀","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"使群花齐放","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"用绵延石山作手臂","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"驱散那满天乌云","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"用纯真的爱","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"要那广野重清","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"把月亮放入眼眶","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"要夜的海闪着蓝光","type":"paragraph"}],"comments":[],"origin":"《重庆市右派言论选辑第一集》（内部文件，只供领导同志参考，请勿外传和翻印），中共重庆市委宣传部办公室编印，1957年8月。","comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":0,"page_end":0,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}